// resolvable" (it requires is_file(), and STM32CubeMX wasn't on PATH
// either). Fixed by updating that registry value to
// C:\Users\13GEN\AppData\Local\Programs\STM32CubeMX\STM32CubeMX.exe;
// verified via resolve_cubemx_launcher() returning that path with
// is_file() == True. Already-running shells/sessions from before the fix
// still see the stale cached value until restarted — new sessions pick it
// up automatically from the registry.
